Mounted tedders are designed to minimize soil compaction and reduce overall environmental impact, making them an eco-friendly choice for farmers.

15. What are the maintenance requirements for mounted tedders?
Maintenance requirements for mounted tedders include regular lubrication, rotor inspection, and replacement of worn-out parts.

